{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9976f14baa","title":"林彪关于部队管理教育的五条指示","origin":"《林彪元帅文集》（下册），香港凤凰书品， 2016年。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c86911634b","index":0,"year":1961,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"9976f14baa"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f31faec50d","type":"title","text":"林彪关于部队管理教育的五条指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9976f14baa"},{"id":"8710b4cf44","type":"paragraph","text":"我军的管理教育工作，必须坚持五条原则：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9976f14baa"},{"id":"a86e4ce0ac","type":"paragraph","text":"一、既要负责管理，严格要求，防止把部队搞得松松垮垮，又要耐心说服教育，讲究方式方法，防止简单粗暴。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9976f14baa"},{"id":"43e1358f3b","type":"paragraph","text":"二、既要以表扬好人好事和进行正面教育为主，又要对一般性的缺点和错误，进行个别谈话或者班、小组的批评。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9976f14baa"},{"id":"5e13292fbb","type":"paragraph","text":"三、既要官管兵，又要动员兵管兵。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9976f14baa"},{"id":"58f9d1d216","type":"paragraph","text":"四、既要进行深入细致的思想工作，又要热情关怀和帮助解决实际困难，干部并应事事以身作则。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9976f14baa"},{"id":"dc736a976a","type":"paragraph","text":"五、既要有严格的军容风纪和正规的生活秩序，又要使部队活泼愉快、官兵融洽无间。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9976f14baa"}],"page":{"id":"9c114ddce7","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9976f14baa","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}